### Test Conflict Detection API
### Sử dụng REST Client extension trong VS Code

### 1. Login để lấy token
POST http://localhost:3002/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-email@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### Save token từ response vào biến
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Tạo Task A
POST http://localhost:3002/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Test Task A - học tiếng anh",
  "description": "Task để test conflict detection",
  "estimatedDuration": 120,
  "dailyTargetDuration": 60,
  "dailyTargetMin": 60,
  "deadline": "2026-03-11T00:00:00.000Z",
  "priority": "high"
}

### Save taskId từ response
@taskAId = TASK_A_ID_HERE

### 3. Tạo Task B
POST http://localhost:3002/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Test Task B - học code",
  "description": "Task để test conflict detection",
  "estimatedDuration": 120,
  "dailyTargetDuration": 60,
  "dailyTargetMin": 60,
  "deadline": "2026-03-11T00:00:00.000Z",
  "priority": "high"
}

### Save taskId từ response
@taskBId = TASK_B_ID_HERE

### 4. AI Schedule Task A (lần đầu - không có conflict)
POST http://localhost:3002/ai/schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskIds": ["{{taskAId}}"],
  "startDate": "2026-03-07T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Expected Response:
### - schedule với Task A có suggestedTime
### - Console log: [Conflict Detection] Found 0 scheduled tasks

### 5. Áp dụng lịch Task A
POST http://localhost:3002/ai/schedule/apply
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "schedule": [
    {
      "taskId": "{{taskAId}}",
      "scheduledTime": {
        "start": "2026-03-07T01:00:00.000Z",
        "end": "2026-03-07T02:00:00.000Z",
        "aiPlanned": true,
        "reason": "Giờ làm việc hiệu quả"
      }
    }
  ]
}

### Expected Response:
### - updated: 1
### - Task A status = "scheduled"

### 6. Verify Task A status
GET http://localhost:3002/tasks/{{taskAId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### - status: "scheduled"
### - scheduledTime.start: "2026-03-07T01:00:00.000Z"
### - scheduledTime.end: "2026-03-07T02:00:00.000Z"

### 7. AI Schedule Task B (có conflict với Task A)
POST http://localhost:3002/ai/schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskIds": ["{{taskBId}}"],
  "startDate": "2026-03-07T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### ⭐ QUAN TRỌNG - Check Backend Console:
### Expected Console Logs:
### [Conflict Detection] Found 1 scheduled tasks
### [Scheduler] Date 2026-03-07: 1 busy slots
### [Scheduler] Task B scheduled at 09:15-10:15 (avoiding Task A)

### Expected Response:
### - Task B có suggestedTime KHÁC với Task A
### - Task B start time > Task A end time + buffer (15 phút)

### 8. Get all scheduled tasks
GET http://localhost:3002/tasks?status=scheduled
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected Response:
### - items array có Task A (và Task B nếu đã apply)
### - Mỗi task có scheduledTime

### 9. Update Task A status manually
PATCH http://localhost:3002/tasks/{{taskAId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Expected Response:
### - status: "in_progress"
### - Success message

### 10. Update Task A status back to scheduled
PATCH http://localhost:3002/tasks/{{taskAId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "scheduled"
}

### Expected Response:
### - status: "scheduled"

### 11. Tạo Task C để test multiple conflicts
POST http://localhost:3002/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Test Task C - tiếng hàn",
  "description": "Task để test multiple conflicts",
  "estimatedDuration": 60,
  "dailyTargetDuration": 60,
  "dailyTargetMin": 60,
  "deadline": "2026-03-11T00:00:00.000Z",
  "priority": "medium"
}

### Save taskId từ response
@taskCId = TASK_C_ID_HERE

### 12. AI Schedule Task C (có conflict với Task A và B)
POST http://localhost:3002/ai/schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskIds": ["{{taskCId}}"],
  "startDate": "2026-03-07T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### ⭐ Check Backend Console:
### Expected Console Logs:
### [Conflict Detection] Found 2 scheduled tasks
### [Scheduler] Date 2026-03-07: 2 busy slots
### [Scheduler] Task C scheduled at 10:30-11:30 (avoiding Task A & B)

### 13. Schedule multiple tasks at once
POST http://localhost:3002/ai/schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "taskIds": ["{{taskAId}}", "{{taskBId}}", "{{taskCId}}"],
  "startDate": "2026-03-07T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Expected Response:
### - All tasks scheduled without conflicts
### - Each task has different time slots
### - Buffer time between tasks

### 14. Delete test tasks (cleanup)
DELETE http://localhost:3002/tasks/{{taskAId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
DELETE http://localhost:3002/tasks/{{taskBId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
DELETE http://localhost:3002/tasks/{{taskCId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Test Complete!
### Nếu tất cả requests pass → Conflict Detection hoạt động hoàn hảo!
